library(tidyverse)
seq(from = -10, to = 10, by = 0.025) %>%
  expand.grid(x = ., y = .) %>%
  ggplot(aes(y = (y + pi * abs(cos(
    x
  )) ^ .5), x = (x + pi * abs(sin(
    y
  )) ^ .5))) +
  geom_point(
    alpha = .01,
    shape = 20,
    size = 0,
    color = "black"
  ) +
  theme_void() + coord_fixed()
